{"tid":465594,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"跑步問題一問","createTime":"2017-11-11T16:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T14:41:27.000Z","uid":6925,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"abba5e60e5ebad9a9bd917094d7555a472fd11d8","tid":465594,"uid":6925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:36:03.000Z","msg":"話說最近半年迷上左慢跑 大概六分鐘1k 每次跑6-7k 前後都會拉筯<br />\n之前個排就發現成日跑跑下右腳會攰過左腳 本來以為係個人側左去右邊身跑 咁就試下側返去左邊，跑跑下又好似冇事<br />\n但最近一次跑步跑跑下覺得右腳小腿前側好緊，同埋每次跑既時間左腳落地好輕力冇聲。右腳每下落地會有聲同埋係成個腳板同時落地，感覺好重，搞到右腳好易攰但左腳又唔會。<br />\n問題黎啦，想問下各位係咪我拉筯拉得唔夠？定係跑既姿勢有錯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求指教下小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9863ef6ab937b2ffbcb03220e5a8c6d7167072a7","tid":465594,"uid":6925,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:39:11.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828135c12e2cc84855e8b99f4358a7faf485c125","tid":465594,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:40:26.000Z","msg":"pash"},{"pid":"9ae1546b2b4e6c8f21b1847fd71cd77619b7ed8d","tid":465594,"uid":6925,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:50:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>pash</blockquote><br />\npesh<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50fb3953a530d5ddff73adc5952d724b4173e3aa","tid":465594,"uid":86288,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:54:46.000Z","msg":"你有冇check過正常足扁平足個d?<br />\n知唔知自己邊隻主力腳？<br />\n落地有冇刻意捻前半腳掌落先？<br />\n有好多因素"},{"pid":"efec2e5c1b248c4835c5b109bc297c18ee19f077","tid":465594,"uid":6925,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T17:01:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你有冇check過正常足扁平足個d?<br />\n知唔知自己邊隻主力腳？<br />\n落地有冇刻意捻前半腳掌落先？<br />\n有好多因素</blockquote><br />\n冇扁平足<br />\n我係左撇 平時都係左手左腳用力多 咁應該係左腳？<br />\n有試過 但就係發現左腳好輕鬆但右腳要好用力先做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nanyway唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814868fa5667adcd95d4c5842b5ef6923062e2d3","tid":465594,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T17:02:39.000Z","msg":"係咪係運動場跑圈?"},{"pid":"d6897479f54cb58d26f18403062b6965f996a437","tid":465594,"uid":6925,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T17:06:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪係運動場跑圈?</blockquote><br />\n係公園d緩跑徑，比較多彎<br />\n之前發現右腳攰d既時候就試下置中咁跑，心理上會覺得有用<br />\n但近排跑就係右腳好快攰，大概2k左右小腿前側就勁崩緊，一定要停低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5749136168a73882d9b2901462848e8f3545670","tid":465594,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T17:06:56.000Z","msg":"你左右足弓對唔對稱架?"},{"pid":"b42c8b77ed147df884900441bfe0de087e3bb4fe","tid":465594,"uid":101231,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T17:08:52.000Z","msg":"試下集中用大腿發力"},{"pid":"2913353bd898055685c1a6c7ee0aca563e32a027","tid":465594,"uid":86288,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T17:09:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你有冇check過正常足扁平足個d?<br />\n知唔知自己邊隻主力腳？<br />\n落地有冇刻意捻前半腳掌落先？<br />\n有好多因素</blockquote><br />\n冇扁平足<br />\n我係左撇 平時都係左手左腳用力多 咁應該係左腳？<br />\n有試過 但就係發現左腳好輕鬆但右腳要好用力先做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nanyway唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同你情況一樣<br />\n左腳正常 右腳dumdum聲<br />\n但唔會右小腿攰<br />\n好大原因係左腳主力腳（我都係）<br />\n係你跑步個陣你唔會sense到每隻腳比嘅力水<br />\n當你址速跑 以為自己兩邊發力一樣<br />\n你左腳因為大力d 踏出嘅距離遠左 令到你右腳比較難腳前掌落翻地<br />\n之前係三聯睇本肌肉骨骼書見到<br />\n未必全對 但可作参考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f5f10b9e98a825e1c8f7a8151542fd613d9432","tid":465594,"uid":6925,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T17:14:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你左右足弓對唔對稱架?</blockquote><br />\n未check過 係咪要去dr kong個d先check到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf1c3039df077132dbaa31e915800e2ae4923bd","tid":465594,"uid":6925,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T17:15:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下集中用大腿發力</blockquote><br />\n好 我下次試下 唔該哂巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167df6b19820cc015b4b3fffa79b15bdf5e79bc7","tid":465594,"uid":6925,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T17:16:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你有冇check過正常足扁平足個d?<br />\n知唔知自己邊隻主力腳？<br />\n落地有冇刻意捻前半腳掌落先？<br />\n有好多因素</blockquote><br />\n冇扁平足<br />\n我係左撇 平時都係左手左腳用力多 咁應該係左腳？<br />\n有試過 但就係發現左腳好輕鬆但右腳要好用力先做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nanyway唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同你情況一樣<br />\n左腳正常 右腳dumdum聲<br />\n但唔會右小腿攰<br />\n好大原因係左腳主力腳（我都係）<br />\n係你跑步個陣你唔會sense到每隻腳比嘅力水<br />\n當你址速跑 以為自己兩邊發力一樣<br />\n你左腳因為大力d 踏出嘅距離遠左 令到你右腳比較難腳前掌落翻地<br />\n之前係三聯睇本肌肉骨骼書見到<br />\n未必全對 但可作参考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n姐係應該跑步個時左腳唔好踏咁大步？<br />\n咁巴打你依家情況有冇改善？<br />\nbtw 唔該哂 經過書局入去望下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"152731487e55e4f6d77ec8b1f3628cd7c3508ded","tid":465594,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T17:37:23.000Z","msg":"唔好跑運動場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試下跑直線就唔會痛<br />\n跑開街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606acd368ada67b74faf95db44f8849c22445966","tid":465594,"uid":6925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T02:48:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好跑運動場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試下跑直線就唔會痛<br />\n跑開街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好 下次試下跑直線 不過慣左夜晚跑所以驚撞到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 唔該曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2338d91c8abf32f2a16bfe3c396925e1a086adb0","tid":465594,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T02:58:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好跑運動場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試下跑直線就唔會痛<br />\n跑開街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n跑場太多灣, 跑街都係一到急D既灣就收步<br />\n<br />\n跑個步唔想傷膝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7683351feeb4a75d3421c7dc2f6eb78cc9c4ffd9","tid":465594,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T07:30:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/UPAHKG/videos/919861511522264/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FUPAHKG%2Fvideos%2F919861511522264%2F&d=f5WNX%2Bhpoj89CKswZk6Y38n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=e55584e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/UPAHKG/videos/919861511522264/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">恭喜迷離哥哥再為埋土贏得賭神稱號<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n數學有望5**並唔係浪得虛名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6f04af62b6a06239f73b6ad8e5cc987334c37d1","tid":465594,"uid":6925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T16:00:58.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39200cede210a996d1ed676cd91d2f70ea492333","tid":465594,"uid":9834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco